Why This "Filesystem as DB" Approach?
Token-Efficient: Instead of feeding a massive, ever-growing context window, the agent only reads relevant memory files.
Transparent and Auditable: The "database" is plain-text markdown, allowing users to read, edit, and fix the agent's knowledge if it becomes confused.
Stateful Agentic Behavior: It enables the AI to move from being reactive (answering a prompt) to proactive (remembering decisions made days prior). 
